data.description: Welcome to this charming 3BR/1BA ranch-style home. This newly renovated gem features three spacious bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation. Step inside and be greeted by the inviting ambiance accentuated by luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, offering both durability & elegance. The heart of this home is adorned w/a cozy gas fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The single bathroom is thoughtfully designed for convenience and comfort, featuring modern fixtures and finishes. This well appointed kitchen is complete w/granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. This home has been thoughtfully outfitted w/new energy-efficient windows. New AC system and furnace promises cool comfort during the summer months, while a new furnace and water heater guarantee cozy warmth throughout the winter. Outside, enjoy the surroundings and soak up the sunshine. Don't miss your chance to make this enchanting retreat your own–schedule a viewing today!
